# This setup provides
    ⚡️ Vite for fast development
    ⚛️ React with TypeScript
    🧪 Vitest for testing with React Testing Library
    🐳 Docker support
    📈 Test coverage reporting
    🛡️ Type safety
    🧩 Modular architecture

Testing Stragegy - Testing Pyramid Strategy

    graph TD
        A[Consumer Tests] --> B[Contract Tests]
        A --> C[Component Tests]
        D[Backend Tests] --> E[Unit Tests]
        D --> F[Integration Tests]
        D --> G[End-to-End Tests]
        B --> D

task-manager/
    ├── task-manager-frontend/     # Vite/React Frontend
    ├── task-manager-backend/      # .NET backend
    └── task-manager-consumer/     # Data layer Package
    └── task-manager-db/           # DB
